title: ‘The Challenge’ Hall of Fame: Laurel Stucky | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is joined by Laurel Stucky to talk about what makes her such a dominant player on ‘The Challenge’ and tell stories from their favorite and least favorite seasons together.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Laurel Stucky
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Juliet Litman
